{"tid":897651,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"睇到綠色和平嘅投票就見到香港人比人洗腦洗得幾嚴重","createTime":"2018-11-11T06:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T22:43:29.000Z","uid":17232,"like":157,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f6706b896a6fc3c2461efda08a8be9eb0620edf5","tid":897651,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T06:08:19.000Z","msg":"話說啱啱見到greenpeace呢個投票，想了解吓香港人覺得最重要嘅環保政策係啲咩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e0SPwLc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe0SPwLc.png&h=66282cdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦撳入去投完去睇結果<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TGmddZY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGmddZY.png&h=f59360e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n煤炭係喺咁多燃料裡面 能量儲存量低之餘，燃燒嘅時候亦都會排放極多嘅二氧化碳同有害物質。點解可以得5%嘅覺得停止燒煤係重要嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我心諗會唔會啲人value其他政策更加重啊？咁我繼續睇落去啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pfw8NjX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPfw8NjX.png&h=acb864a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吓？發展潔淨可再生能源竟然得10%人覺得重要？ <br />\n<br />\n香港人知唔知呢個地球有7成嘅溫室氣體排放係因為用化石燃料發電而排放出黎？ <br />\n<br />\n知唔知如果地球全面發展可再生能源係可以完全舒緩全球暖化呢個最大嘅環保議題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後，<br />\n<br />\n我懷住完全失望嘅心情撳落去最多人投嘅一個選項，睇吓香港人覺得最重要嘅環保政策係咩。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1zBgWdk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1zBgWdk.png&h=ec205806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌你老母啊？ 全城覺醒夠鐘走塑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"ad0b9f61ece2205df81ce93f56d4e367c22697ee","tid":897651,"uid":33507,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T06:10:47.000Z","msg":"港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48624f93aaaea92a631c65d8db350fedd4d499bf","tid":897651,"uid":17232,"like":70,"dislike":4,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T06:13:33.000Z","msg":"有時我真係覺得地球嘅環境就係比呢啲環保撚害撚死。大家唔去關注一啲真真正正舒緩地球環境嘅野，例如潔淨能源啊，減低溫室氣體排放啊。但係就比啲環保撚/大商家shift左個關注去啲細微細眼啊，飲野唔撚用飲管，全民走塑呢啲on9野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n地球嘅環境就係咁撚樣比啲環保撚害死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35eeccca0c177583f7bffc79ecda8aa7e4f1185","tid":897651,"uid":42460,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T06:14:48.000Z","msg":"有少少sense 都唔會填依啲19問卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而會填個問卷又唔方有sense"},{"pid":"a17c359ffc53e98af4f9c1511eba749918b838cb","tid":897651,"uid":17232,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T06:18:35.000Z","msg":"塑膠當你唔處理佢地嘅時候頂多只係一個固體廢物棄置嘅問題。就算係焚燒所造成嘅空氣污染對比起全球燃燒化石燃料排放嘅有害氣體都只係九牛一毛。塑膠問題喺環保議題裡面點都只不過係second priority啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a757641e10e02de4376e75f8c13e8490ee2517","tid":897651,"uid":34184,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T06:19:16.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪想推向大陸買&ldquo;乾淨&rdquo;的核電<br />\n<br />\n香港兩電開始俾環保撚迫死<br />\n<br />\n遲早退出香港等樓豬日日人力發電"},{"pid":"803a3938541e40e80deff577343ddf01e9b86816","tid":897651,"uid":140979,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"c35eeccca0c177583f7bffc79ecda8aa7e4f1185","tid":897651,"uid":42460,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T06:14:48.000Z","msg":"有少少sense 都唔會填依啲19問卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而會填個問卷又唔方有sense"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T06:19:37.000Z","msg":"大部份環保撚都真係無sense<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ad060987d6953b39f9833f5ffd6d668b9a4c59","tid":897651,"uid"